{"tid":2135462,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴打馬會做善事 送錢比我哋洗","createTime":"2020-08-01T12:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T18:41:44.000Z","uid":195009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"61739fea5effa768fe863c2bfd317a04fc50bdb0","tid":2135462,"uid":195009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YSB77G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YSB77G.png&h=2b0c1297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正常大家都記得上年歐霸總決賽車仔勁炒阿記4:1喎 所以話總決賽點可以唔買車仔？<br />\n同埋近排車仔個勢超好 前鋒有靚仔神射手基奧特 一落場實㩒住後衛25仔雷斯嚟打 仲要有快馬韋利安 世三美隊一扭五再入波<br />\n<br />\n相反阿記淨係得水貨比比 回塘奧巴美羊 鳩射鳩傳嘅嘅拿卡 仲要有個後防廢到仆街自爆嘅雷斯 <br />\n加上大家睇下聯賽積分榜 車仔排第四喎 阿記第八 都勁兩倍啦  <br />\n所以我真係唔明點解唔重注車仔 <br />\n馬會真係做福大家 知道個市道唔好 特登送錢比我哋洗 多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0842e170af598b4bc13e815d2271c7282ec732d8","tid":2135462,"uid":195009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664a606a9af56f347da19a5943cbc3048545a947","tid":2135462,"uid":195009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb153959b06990b946d3360f21ea7c471d5c434","tid":2135462,"uid":195009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"上車趁而家"},{"pid":"170339b1a785980b8c473a23fade575c5f261fde","tid":2135462,"uid":195009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac